52 namespace fastrack {

54 
55 class QuadrotorControlBoundBox : public ControlBound<QuadrotorControl> {
56  public:
57  ~QuadrotorControlBoundBox() {}
58  explicit QuadrotorControlBoundBox(const QuadrotorControl& min,
59  const QuadrotorControl& max)
60  : pitch_interval_(min.pitch, max.pitch),
61  roll_interval_(min.roll, max.roll),
62  yaw_rate_interval_(min.yaw_rate, max.yaw_rate),
63  thrust_interval_(min.thrust, max.thrust) {}
64 
65  // Assume params are laid out as follows:
66  // [min pitch, min roll, min yaw rate, min thrust,
67  // max pitch, max roll, max yaw rate, max thrust]
68  explicit QuadrotorControlBoundBox(const std::vector<double>& params)
69  : pitch_interval_(params[0], params[4]),
70  roll_interval_(params[1], params[5]),
71  yaw_rate_interval_(params[2], params[6]),
72  thrust_interval_(params[3], params[7]) {}
73 
74  // Custom definition of copy-assign operator.
75  QuadrotorControlBoundBox& operator=(const QuadrotorControlBoundBox& other) {
76  if (&other == this) return *this;
77 
78  pitch_interval_ = other.pitch_interval_;
79  roll_interval_ = other.roll_interval_;
80  yaw_rate_interval_ = other.yaw_rate_interval_;
81  thrust_interval_ = other.thrust_interval_;
82  return *this;
83  }
84 
85  // Derived classes must be able to check whether a query is inside the
86  // bound.
87  inline bool Contains(const QuadrotorControl& query) const {
88  return pitch_interval_.Contains(query.pitch) &&
89  roll_interval_.Contains(query.roll) &&
90  yaw_rate_interval_.Contains(query.yaw_rate) &&
91  thrust_interval_.Contains(query.thrust);
92  }
93 
94  // Derived classes must be able to compute the projection of a vector
95  // (represented as the templated type) onto the surface of the bound.
96  // NOTE: this is basically solving an LP with the bound as the feasible
97  // set and the query as the coefficients.
98  inline QuadrotorControl ProjectToSurface(
99  const QuadrotorControl& query) const {
100  return QuadrotorControl(pitch_interval_.ProjectToSurface(query.pitch),
101  roll_interval_.ProjectToSurface(query.roll),
102  yaw_rate_interval_.ProjectToSurface(query.yaw_rate),
103  thrust_interval_.ProjectToSurface(query.thrust));
104  }
105 
106  private:
107  // ScalarBoundIntervals for each control variable.
108  ScalarBoundInterval pitch_interval_;
109  ScalarBoundInterval roll_interval_;
110  ScalarBoundInterval yaw_rate_interval_;
111  ScalarBoundInterval thrust_interval_;
112 }; //\class ControlBound
113
